<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <title>Automobile - Natalia, l'assistante IA pour les concessions</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Natalia repond, transfere et assiste vos clients 24/7. Solution IA pour concessions automobiles.">
  <%- include('./includes/_head.ejs') %>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen flex flex-col">
<%- include('./includes/_header.ejs') %>

<main class="flex-grow">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="section bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-primary/5 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="gradient-orb gradient-orb-1"></div>
    <div class="gradient-orb gradient-orb-2"></div>
    <div class="container-content relative z-10">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h1 class="hero-title text-h1-mobile md:text-h1 font-bold text-police-titre mb-4">
            Natalia repond,
            <span class="text-gradient">transfere et assiste</span>
            vos clients 24/7
          </h1>
          <p class="hero-subtitle text-lg text-police-grey font-semibold mb-8">
            Une voix naturelle, une comprehension instantanee et une integration fluide a vos outils metiers automobiles
          </p>
          <div class="hero-cta">
            <a href="./contact" class="btn btn-primary inline-flex items-center gap-2">
              Reserver une demo
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-image flex justify-center">
          <div class="relative animate-float-slow">
            <img src="./assets/images/automobilePng2.png" alt="Concession automobile IA" class="w-full max-w-lg rounded-xl shadow-lg glow">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Quote Section -->
  <section class="section bg-primary/5">
    <div class="container-content text-center">
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-police-grey max-w-4xl mx-auto animate-on-scroll">
        <strong>40% des appels en concession ne sont pas traites.</strong> Entre les clients en showroom, les appels simultanes et les standardistes debordees, de nombreuses opportunites sont perdues.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Problemes Section -->
  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container-content">
      <h2 class="text-h2-mobile md:text-h2 font-bold text-police-titre text-center mb-12 animate-on-scroll">
        Vos <span class="text-gradient">defis</span> quotidiens
      </h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6" data-stagger>
        <div class="card border-l-4 border-l-red-500">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 mb-4 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-red-100 text-red-600">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-police-titre mb-2">Appels manques</h3>
          <p class="text-police-grey text-sm">
            Vos standardistes sont occupees avec les clients en showroom. Les appels sonnent dans le vide, les clients raccrochent.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card border-l-4 border-l-orange-500">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 mb-4 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-orange-100 text-orange-600">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-police-titre mb-2">Horaires limites</h3>
          <p class="text-police-grey text-sm">
            Les clients appellent en dehors des heures d'ouverture, pendant la pause dejeuner ou le week-end.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card border-l-4 border-l-yellow-500">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 mb-4 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-600">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-6 9l2 2 4-4"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-police-titre mb-2">Prise de RDV</h3>
          <p class="text-police-grey text-sm">
            La prise de RDV atelier est chronophage et source d'erreurs. Les plannings ne sont pas toujours a jour.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card border-l-4 border-l-purple-500">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 mb-4 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-purple-100 text-purple-600">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-police-titre mb-2">Leads perdus</h3>
          <p class="text-police-grey text-sm">
            Les prospects qui n'arrivent pas a joindre la concession vont voir la concurrence.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Quote Section 2 -->
  <section class="section bg-police-titre text-white">
    <div class="container-content text-center">
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl max-w-4xl mx-auto animate-on-scroll">
        Chaque appel manque est une opportunite perdue. Chaque client qui raccroche est peut-etre <strong>une vente de vehicule ou un entretien qui s'envole.</strong>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Solutions Section -->
  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container-content">
      <h2 class="text-h2-mobile md:text-h2 font-bold text-police-titre text-center mb-12 animate-on-scroll">
        Nos <span class="text-gradient">solutions</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6" data-stagger-scale>
        <div class="card text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-police-titre mb-2">Disponible 24/7</h3>
          <p class="text-police-grey text-sm">
            Natalia repond aux appels meme en dehors des heures d'ouverture, pendant les pauses et les week-ends.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-secondary/10 text-secondary">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-police-titre mb-2">Prise de RDV</h3>
          <p class="text-police-grey text-sm">
            Connectee a Service Box ou MecaPlanning, Natalia propose des creneaux et valide les RDV directement.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-green-100 text-green-600">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-police-titre mb-2">Transfert intelligent</h3>
          <p class="text-police-grey text-sm">
            Natalia identifie le besoin et transfere vers le bon service : VN, VO, SAV, pieces detachees.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-blue-100 text-blue-600">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 9l3 3-3 3m5 0h3M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-police-titre mb-2">Integree</h3>
          <p class="text-police-grey text-sm">
            Connectee a vos DMS (Nextlane, CDK Global, DC's Net, etc.) pour une synchronisation parfaite.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Compatible Section -->
  <section class="section bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container-content">
      <h2 class="text-h2-mobile md:text-h2 font-bold text-police-titre text-center mb-4 animate-on-scroll">
        Compatible avec vos <span class="text-gradient">outils metiers</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-center text-police-grey mb-12 animate-on-scroll">
        Integration native avec les principales solutions du secteur automobile
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center items-center gap-8 md:gap-12 animate-on-scroll">
        <img src="./assets/images/nextlanePng.png" alt="Nextlane" class="h-10 md:h-14 object-contain opacity-70 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">
        <img src="./assets/images/logoMpaPng.png" alt="MPA" class="h-10 md:h-14 object-contain opacity-70 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Cas d'usage Section -->
  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container-content">
      <div class="text-center mb-12 animate-on-scroll">
        <h2 class="text-h2-mobile md:text-h2 font-bold text-police-titre mb-4">
          Cas d'usage <span class="text-gradient">concrets</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-police-grey max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          L'objectif n'est pas de remplacer l'humain en concession mais de l'<strong>assister pour qu'il se concentre sur les missions a forte valeur ajoutee</strong>. Avec ces 4 cas d'usage, nous repondons a <strong>80% des besoins en appels entrants en concession</strong>.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6" data-stagger-scale>
        <div class="card bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/5 to-primary/10 border border-primary/20">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 mb-4 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary text-white">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-police-titre mb-2">Prise de RDV atelier</h3>
          <p class="text-police-grey text-sm">
            Connectee a votre calendrier metier, Natalia propose des creneaux, valide avec le client et renseigne les informations directement sur le logiciel.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary/5 to-secondary/10 border border-secondary/20">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 mb-4 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-secondary text-white">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-police-titre mb-2">Qualifier les leads</h3>
          <p class="text-police-grey text-sm">
            Natalia prend en charge 100% des demandes entrants. Durant l'echange, elle qualifie le besoin et renvoie les informations au service concerne.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-green-100 border border-green-200">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 mb-4 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-green-500 text-white">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-police-titre mb-2">Transfert d'appels</h3>
          <p class="text-police-grey text-sm">
            20% des appels en concession sont des appels a transferer, cela prend du temps et casse la productivite de vos equipes.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-50 to-orange-100 border border-orange-200">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 mb-4 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-orange-500 text-white">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-police-titre mb-2">Demandes generales</h3>
          <p class="text-police-grey text-sm">
            Reponse aux demandes recurrentes a partir de votre base de connaissance. Natalia s'enrichit dans le temps.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="section bg-gradient-animated text-white relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-64 h-64 bg-white/5 rounded-full -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 animate-float"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-white/5 rounded-full translate-x-1/3 translate-y-1/3 animate-float" style="animation-delay: 2s;"></div>
    <div class="container-content text-center relative z-10">
      <h2 class="text-h2-mobile md:text-h2 font-bold mb-6 text-white animate-on-scroll">
        Nous definissons ensemble le cadre du pilote lors d'un premier rendez-vous.
      </h2>
      <div class="animate-on-scroll">
        <a href="./contact" class="btn btn-white inline-flex items-center gap-2">
          Reserver une demo
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<%- include('./includes/_footer.ejs') %>

</body>
</html>
